To be more specific, instead of:

library(parallel)
cl <- ... # Make a cluster
parLapply(cl, X, fun, ...)

you can do:

library(parallel)
library(doParallel)
library(plyr)
cl <- ...
registerDoParallel(cl)
llply(X, fun, ..., .parallel=TRUE)

